summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Seattle Public Utilities; authorizing grants of easements over, under and across portions of properties known as the Lake Youngs Tunnel right of way, the Lake Youngs By Pass \#4 right of way and the Lake Youngs Control Works property, all located in Section 27, Township 23 North, Range 5 East, W.M., in King County, Washington, and establishing the fair market value thereof.
committee: Water Resources, Solid Waste and Public Health
